snippet.title: Terry's Treasure Trouble! Trailer
snippet.description:
It's still taking its time to get there, but dang it, I'm still working on this game. This includes music, graphics, gameplay and code, and overcoming my struggles with sticking with it, including bouts of depression.

Terry's Treasure Trouble is my attempt at making the ultimate Hop 'n' Bop platform game. It combines elements of Mario, Sonic, and Donkey Kong Country, and features many gimmicky elements. Our cartoon character goes seeking out treasure on the Feyside Islands, but Grand Beard's pirates are after it, too. Will anyone find the treasure?

The sound effects hopefully will get an upgrade later, if everything works out as intended.
